<div class="image"><img width="701" height="526" src="http://www.oert.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/T03A_16-cargafuentes_fontexplorer.jpg" class="attachment-large" alt="Cargar fuentes eb FontExplorer: paso 4" />
</div></li>
<li>
<div class="image"><img width="701" height="526" src="http://www.oert.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/T03A_15-cargafuentes_fontexplorer.jpg" class="attachment-large" alt="Cargar fuentes eb FontExplorer: paso 3" />
</div><div class="description">Cargar fuentes en FontExplorer</div>
</li>
<li>
<div class="image"><img width="701" height="526" src="http://www.oert.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/T03A_14-cargafuentes_fontexplorer.jpg" class="attachment-large" alt="Cargar fuentes eb FontExplorer: paso 2" />
</div><div class="description">Cargar fuentes en FontExplorer</div>
</li>
